           SHORT="DVD Transcoder for Unix"
cat << EOF
Drip is a DVD to DIVX conversion application. It's made up out two
applications: a DVD reader and a DIVX encoder. The reader is a GUI for the
GNOME environment, the DIVX encoder a text mode tool. You wont have to learn to
use the textmode tool, because the GUI also is a frontend for it.
EOF

  
